text: What's my favorite type of sandwich you ask? Well, it's a sub, of course. Hello, sweetheart. I'm Sheebie Cottonbum, the ever-demanding madame and mistress of Euler's Gen 1 indulge. Come down the rabbit hole and I'll show you my wonderland, maybe. I just can't wait to show you the ropes.
